### Component 3: Auth App

JWT authentication with custom token generation, role-based permissions.

---

#### [NEW] [apps/auth_app/views.py](file:///home/bastard/Desktop/b_hB1FLZHsGiY-1774459584029/hms_backend/apps/auth_app/views.py)
Three views:
- `LoginView` — validates credentials against `Staff` doc, generates JWT pair with `user_id`, `role`, `hospital_id`, `jti` in payload, stores refresh token hash
- `RefreshTokenView` — rotates refresh token, issues new access token
- `LogoutView` — blacklists access token JTI, revokes refresh token

#### [NEW] [apps/auth_app/serializers.py](file:///home/bastard/Desktop/b_hB1FLZHsGiY-1774459584029/hms_backend/apps/auth_app/serializers.py)
`LoginSerializer`, `RefreshSerializer`, `LogoutSerializer` — input validation.

#### [NEW] [apps/auth_app/permissions.py](file:///home/bastard/Desktop/b_hB1FLZHsGiY-1774459584029/hms_backend/apps/auth_app/permissions.py)
Custom DRF permission classes: `IsReceptionist`, `IsConsultant`, `IsDoctor`, `IsPharmacy`, `IsAnyStaff`. Also a custom `JWTAuthentication` class that validates JWT, checks blacklist, and attaches user info to `request.user`.

#### [NEW] [apps/auth_app/urls.py](file:///home/bastard/Desktop/b_hB1FLZHsGiY-1774459584029/hms_backend/apps/auth_app/urls.py)
Routes: `auth/login/`, `auth/refresh/`, `auth/logout/`.

