Replace demo mode login with real API call to `POST /api/v1/auth/login/`. Store JWT tokens in localStorage. Add token refresh logic. Keep `isDemo` flag as `false`.

#### [MODIFY] Multiple page files
For each page that uses `store.*` from `demo-store.ts`:
- Replace with API calls from `api-client.ts`
- Map response shapes to match existing component expectations
- Keep all UI structure, components, and styling untouched
- Only change data fetching logic

